# 15 per row
TILE_1333=(1x1 2x1 2x2 2x2 3x2 3x2 3x3 3x3 3x3 4x3 4x3 4x3 4x4 4x4 4x4 \
4x4 5x4 5x4 5x4 5x4 5x5 5x5 5x5 5x5 5x5 6x5 6x5 6x5 6x5 6x5 \
